msgid "Cookie banner content"
msgstr ""
"This website uses cookies to improve your experience on our website. By "
"clicking вҖңAccept All CookiesвҖқ, you consent to our use of cookies. You can"
" read more in our"

msgid "Cookie Policy"
msgstr "Cookie Policy"

msgid "Cookies Settings"
msgstr "Cookies Settings"

msgid "Cookies Details"
msgstr "Cookies Details"

msgid "Accept All Cookies"
msgstr "Accept All Cookies"

msgid "Privacy Preference Center"
msgstr "Privacy Preference Center"

msgid "Privacy Preference Center content"
msgstr ""
"When you visit any website, it may store or retrieve information on your "
"browser, mostly in the form of cookies. This information might be about "
"you, your preferences or your device and is mostly used to make the site "
"work as you expect it to. The information does not usually directly "
"identify you, but it can give you a more personalized web experience. "
"Because we respect your right to privacy, you can choose not to allow "
"some types of cookies. Click on the different category headings to find "
"out more and change our default settings. However, blocking some types of"
" cookies may impact your experience of the site and the services we are "
"able to offer."

msgid "More information"
msgstr "More information"

msgid "Manage Consent Preferences"
msgstr "Manage Consent Preferences"

msgid "Strictly Necessary Cookies"
msgstr "Strictly Necessary Cookies"

msgid "Strictly Necessary Cookies description"
msgstr ""
"These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be "
"switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to "
"actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as "
"setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can"
" set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some "
"parts of the site will not then work. These cookies do not store any "
"personally identifiable information."

msgid "Targeting Cookies"
msgstr "Targeting Cookies"

msgid "Targeting Cookies description"
msgstr ""
"These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. "
"They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests "
"and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly "
"personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser "
"and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will "
"experience less targeted advertising."

msgid "Functional Cookies"
msgstr "Functional Cookies"

msgid "Functional Cookies description"
msgstr ""
"These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and "
"personalisation. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose "
"services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies "
"then some or all of these services may not function properly."

msgid "Performance Cookies"
msgstr "Performance Cookies"

msgid "Performance Cookies description"
msgstr ""
"These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can "
"measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know "
"which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move "
"around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and "
"therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know "
"when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its "
"performance."

msgid "Confirm My Choices"
msgstr "Confirm My Choices"

msgid "Allow All"
msgstr "Allow All"

msgid "Cookie List"
msgstr "Cookie List"

