"\n"
"e.g.) 1 week = 168, 30 days = 720, a half year = 4320, one year = 8760"

#: ap/templates/macros.html
msgid "Window length Hover AgP"
msgstr ""
"Enter the time width for calculating one plot or summary result. Please "
"enter a number between 0.01 (=36 seconds) and less than 20,000 (=833 "
