msgid "ProcessConfigFilterHover"
msgstr ""
"Data will be imported based on the values entered here. Regular "
"expressions can be used.\n"
"For example, use\n"
"\"\"   вҖңabcвҖқ to search for items containing вҖңabcвҖқ (partial match),\n"
"   вҖң^abcвҖқ to find items starting with вҖңabcвҖқ,\n"
"   вҖң^abc$вҖқ for items matching вҖңabcвҖқ (exact match),\n"
"   вҖңab|cвҖқ to search for items containing either вҖңabвҖқ or вҖңcвҖқ (OR "
"condition), and\n"
"   вҖң^(?!test|abc).*вҖқ to find items starting something other than вҖңtestвҖқ "
"or вҖңabcвҖқ.\n"
"(вҖң^вҖқ indicates that the next character is at the beginning, вҖң$вҖқ indicates"
" that the preceding character is at the end, and вҖң|вҖқ means OR.\n"
"Note: The quotation marks are not needed when entering the values.)"

